      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASH WORTH (6) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at this track and distance (22.85) after forging to the front and leading throughout, scoring by 0.8 lengths. Rates on top again. BETTY EMGRAND (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (18.92) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Should play a prominent role. SUPER SEQUIN (3) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Jamal Wick (23.09) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Leading chance. LAYLA'S LILLY (2) was a last-start winner at big odds and can go on with it.",
